    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/加入我们（简中）.png?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/qq跳转页圆角.png?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/600.50分割线2.png?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/游戏介绍（简中）.png?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><br>在这个友谊小船说翻就翻的游戏中，玩家会面临随机展开的不同类型比赛，用默契的配合和细致的操作突围而出，淘汰其他队伍，走向冠军宝座。<br><br>叫上你默契十足的小伙伴们与其他玩家展开精彩的乱斗吧！<br><br>和队友商量好对策，小心狡诈的敌人，同时更要提防身边的那位猪队友！或许队友才是你夺冠路上最大的绊脚石。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人在线竞技，淘汰对手生存下去！</h2>游戏2人一队，一共进行3轮，每一轮淘汰4队玩家，最后一轮中击败其他队伍的玩家队伍将获得“最佳搭档”称号，每一个关卡都充满乐趣和挑战，考验着你们之间的默契程度。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最佳搭档？最佳损友？</h2>很多神奇而有趣的时刻，让你发现最大的敌人可能是身边那位“最佳损友”。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握生存技巧</h2>闯关的关卡会越来越难，需要在闯关的过程中掌握更多游戏技巧和提高与搭档的默契度噢。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赢下金币来装扮自己吧</h2>每局获胜都会取得相应的金币奖励，可以到商店美美地打扮一番~（有各种情侣/亲子装噢）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/关卡预览（简中）_.png?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/水上乐园.gif?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/武道.gif?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904120/extras/计算器.gif?t=1681271971\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class